name: Episode 3/3: The choice
description:
In the end, life is about choices. Every choice we make, every decision we take, there always be the consequences. Keep exploring and learning, make mistakes, take a lesson from it. Trust the process, be patience, and then it's matter of time.

Endure, endure, endure, ensure
(Terbentur, terbentur, terbentur, terbentuk) 
-Tan Malaka-
